CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[GenerateResetToken]
@ResetToken VARCHAR(250),
@ResetTokenExpiryTime datetime,
@EmailId VARCHAR(200)
AS
BEGIN
   UPDATE UserInfo SET ResetToken = @ResetToken, ResetTokenExpiryTime = @ResetTokenExpiryTime WHERE EmailId = @EmailId
  
END;

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[GetDocumentReviewStatus]    Script Date: 3/28/2025 11:25:55 AM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[GetDocumentReviewStatus] --GetPivotedDocumentComments want change name sp 
AS
BEGIN
    DECLARE @cols NVARCHAR(MAX), @query NVARCHAR(MAX);

    -- Step 1: Get unique Vessel Names as column headers
    SET @cols = STUFF((SELECT DISTINCT ', [' + VesselName + ']'
                        FROM Vessels
                        FOR XML PATH(''), TYPE).value('.', 'NVARCHAR(MAX)'), 1, 2, '');

    -- Step 2: Construct the dynamic pivot query
    SET @query = '
    WITH SourceTable AS (
        SELECT 
            d.Document_Title, 
            v.VesselName, 
            CASE 
                WHEN COUNT(dc.Id) > 0 
                     AND DATEDIFF(MONTH, MAX(dc.CreatedDate), GETDATE()) <= 
                         (SELECT MAX(rps.MaximumMonthsAllowed) 
                          FROM ReviewPolicySetting rps 
                          WHERE rps.IsActive=1 and rps.CategoryId = d.Category_Id) 
                THEN N''Yes''  -- If comment exists and is within allowed months
                ELSE N''No''   -- No comment or exceeds allowed months
            END AS Comments
        FROM Document d
        CROSS JOIN Vessels v
        LEFT JOIN dbo.DocumentComments dc  
            ON dc.Vessel_Id = v.Id 
            AND dc.Document_Id = d.Document_Id
        GROUP BY d.Document_Title, v.VesselName, d.Category_Id
    ) 
    SELECT Document_Title, ' + @cols + ' 
    FROM SourceTable
    PIVOT (
        MAX(Comments) FOR VesselName IN (' + @cols + ')
    ) AS PivotTable
    ORDER BY Document_Title desc;';

    -- Step 3: Execute the dynamic SQL query
    EXEC sp_executesql @query;
END;

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[InsertApprovedRevisionToDocument]
AS
BEGIN
    SET NOCOUNT ON;

    -- Insert latest approved revision into Document table
    INSERT INTO [dbo].[Document] (
        [Revision_Id], [Category_Id], [SubCategoryString], [Document_Number], 
        [Document_Title],  [Publisher_Date], [Valid_From], 
        [Language_Id], [VesselRank_Id], [Vessels_Id], [Department_Id], 
        [Author], [Approved_By], [Document_File_Name], [Document_Text], 
        [ReviewBy], [Status], [Document_Description], [Current_Version], 
        [ChangeInThisVersion], [InternalNotes], [Reference_Title], [Reference_Link], 
        [CreatedDate], [CreatedBy], [ModifiedDate], [ModifiedBy], [IsActive]
    )
    SELECT 
        r.[Revision_Id], r.[Category_Id], r.[SubCategoryString], r.[Document_Number], 
        r.[Document_Title],  r.[Publisher_Date], r.[Valid_From], 
        r.[Language_Id], r.[VesselRank_Id], r.[Vessels_Id], r.[Department_Id], 
        r.[Author], r.[Approved_By], r.[Document_File_Name], r.[Document_Text], 
        r.[ReviewBy], r.[Status], r.[Document_Description], r.[Current_Version], 
        r.[ChangeInThisVersion], r.[InternalNotes], r.[Reference_Title], r.[Reference_Link], 
        GETDATE(), r.[CreatedBy], GETDATE(), r.[ModifiedBy], r.[IsActive]
    FROM [dbo].[Revision] r
    WHERE r.[Status] = 'Approved' 
        AND r.[Revision_Id] = (
            SELECT MAX(Revision_Id) 
            FROM [dbo].[Revision] 
            WHERE [Status] = 'Approved'
        );
END;

create PROCEDURE [dbo].[SP_FleetMasters]
    @ActionType NVARCHAR(10), -- 'INSERT', 'UPDATE', 'DELETE', 'GET'
    @TableType NVARCHAR(10),  -- 'FleetType' OR 'FleetName'
    @Id INT = NULL,           -- Tid or Fid
    @Name NVARCHAR(255) = NULL,
    @AddedBy NVARCHAR(255) = NULL
AS
BEGIN
    SET NOCOUNT ON;

    IF @TableType = 'FleetType'
    BEGIN
        IF @ActionType = 'INSERT'
        BEGIN
            INSERT INTO FleetType (FleetType, AddedBy) 
            VALUES (@Name, @AddedBy);
        END
        ELSE IF @ActionType = 'UPDATE'
        BEGIN
            UPDATE FleetType 
            SET FleetType = @Name, AddedBy = @AddedBy
            WHERE Tid = @Id;
        END
        ELSE IF @ActionType = 'DELETE'
        BEGIN
            DELETE FROM FleetType WHERE Tid = @Id;
        END
        ELSE IF @ActionType = 'GET'
        BEGIN
            SELECT * FROM FleetType WHERE Tid = @Id OR @Id IS NULL;
        END
    END

    ELSE IF @TableType = 'FleetName'
    BEGIN
        IF @ActionType = 'INSERT'
        BEGIN
            INSERT INTO FleetName (FleetName, AddedBy) 
            VALUES (@Name, @AddedBy);
        END
        ELSE IF @ActionType = 'UPDATE'
        BEGIN
            UPDATE FleetName 
            SET FleetName = @Name, AddedBy = @AddedBy
            WHERE Fid = @Id;
        END
        ELSE IF @ActionType = 'DELETE'
        BEGIN
            DELETE FROM FleetName WHERE Fid = @Id;
        END
        ELSE IF @ActionType = 'GET'
        BEGIN
            SELECT * FROM FleetName WHERE Fid = @Id OR @Id IS NULL;
        END
    END
END;

GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[sp_GetDocumentCommentsWithVesselName]
    @ActionType NVARCHAR(10),  -- 'getall' or 'getbyid'
    @DocumentId INT = NULL     -- Used only for 'getbyid'
AS
BEGIN
    SET NOCOUNT ON;

    IF @ActionType = 'getall'
    BEGIN
        -- Get all commented documents
        SELECT 
		   dc.Id,
            v.VesselName,
            dc.VesselComment_Attachment,
            dc.Comments,
            d.Current_Version AS Revision,
            dc.Status
        FROM DocumentComments dc
        INNER JOIN Document d ON dc.Document_Id = d.Document_Id
        INNER JOIN Vessels v ON dc.Vessel_Id = v.Id 
        WHERE (dc.Comments IS NOT NULL AND LTRIM(RTRIM(dc.Comments)) <> '');
    END
    ELSE IF @ActionType = 'getbyid' AND @DocumentId IS NOT NULL
    BEGIN
        -- Get comments for a specific document
        SELECT 
		    dc.Id,
            v.VesselName,
            dc.VesselComment_Attachment,
            dc.Comments,
            d.Current_Version AS Revision,
            dc.Status
        FROM DocumentComments dc
        INNER JOIN Document d ON dc.Document_Id = d.Document_Id
        INNER JOIN Vessels v ON dc.Vessel_Id = v.Id 
        WHERE dc.Document_Id = @DocumentId
          AND (dc.Comments IS NOT NULL AND LTRIM(RTRIM(dc.Comments)) <> '');
    END
    ELSE
    BEGIN
        -- Handle invalid cases
        PRINT 'Invalid action type or missing DocumentId';
    END
END

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[sp_GetDocumentNamefromJson]    Script Date: 3/28/2025 11:25:55 AM ******/

create proc [dbo].[sp_GetDocumentNamefromJson] --  sp_GetDocumentNamefromJson 35, '1. POLICIES'
@CategoryId int = null,
@SubCatName nvarchar(300) = null
as


WITH Parent AS (
    -- Extract first-level objects (BMM level)
    SELECT *
    FROM OPENJSON((SELECT categoryjson FROM SubCategory where categoryid=@CategoryId and IsActive=1), '$')
    WITH (
        parent_name NVARCHAR(255) '$.name',
        children NVARCHAR(MAX) '$.children' AS JSON
    )
),
Policies AS (
    -- Extract second-level objects (1. POLICIES level)
    SELECT *
    FROM Parent
    CROSS APPLY OPENJSON(children)
    WITH (
        policy_name NVARCHAR(255) '$.name',
        policy_children NVARCHAR(MAX) '$.children' AS JSON
    )
    --WHERE policy_name = '1. POLICIES'
	WHERE policy_name = @SubCatName
)
-- Extract third-level objects (SAFE NAVIGATION level)
SELECT id, name, approval
FROM Policies
CROSS APPLY OPENJSON(policy_children)
WITH (
    id INT '$.id',
    name NVARCHAR(255) '$.name',
    approval INT '$.approval'
);

create PROCEDURE [dbo].[sp_ManageCategory]
    @Action NVARCHAR(20),  
    @Id INT = NULL,
    @CategoryName NVARCHAR(300) = NULL,
    @Description NVARCHAR(MAX) = NULL,
    @ContainsManual BIT = NULL,
    @CreatedDate DATETIME = NULL,
    @CreatedBy NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
    @ModifiedDate DATETIME = NULL,
    @ModifiedBy NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
    @IsActive BIT = NULL
AS
BEGIN
    SET NOCOUNT ON;

    -- Insert Category
    IF @Action = 'INSERT'
    BEGIN
        INSERT INTO Category (CategoryName, Description, ContainsManual, CreatedDate, CreatedBy, ModifiedDate, ModifiedBy, IsActive)
        VALUES (@CategoryName, @Description, @ContainsManual, @CreatedDate, @CreatedBy, @ModifiedDate, @ModifiedBy, @IsActive);

        -- Return the newly inserted Category ID
        SELECT SCOPE_IDENTITY() AS NewCategoryID;
    END

    -- Update Category
    ELSE IF @Action = 'UPDATE'
    BEGIN
        UPDATE Category
        SET 
            CategoryName = @CategoryName,
            Description = @Description,
            ContainsManual = @ContainsManual,
            ModifiedDate = @ModifiedDate,
            ModifiedBy = @ModifiedBy,
            IsActive = @IsActive
        WHERE Id = @Id;
    END

    -- Delete Category
    ELSE IF @Action = 'DELETE'
    BEGIN
       -- DELETE FROM Category WHERE Id = @Id;
	   update Category set IsActive=0 where Id=@Id
    END

    -- Get All Categories
    ELSE IF @Action = 'GET_ALL'
    BEGIN
        SELECT * FROM Category where IsActive=1;
    END

    -- Get Category by ID
    ELSE IF @Action = 'GET_BY_ID'

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[sp_ManageCircular]

	@Archive_Reason  NVARCHAR(MAX) = NULL,
    @Auto_Archived_Date DATETIME = NULL,
	@Archived_By NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
    @Circular_Status NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
	@Archive_Date DATETIME = NULL,
    @CreatedDate DATETIME = NULL,
    @CreatedBy NVARCHAR(50) = NULL,
    @ModifiedDate DATETIME = NULL,
    @ModifiedBy NVARCHAR(50) = NULL,
    @IsActive BIT = NULL
AS
BEGIN
    SET NOCOUNT ON;

    IF @Action = 'Insert'
    BEGIN
        INSERT INTO [dbo].[Circular] ([Vessels_Id],
            [Department_Id], [Vessel], [VesselTypes_Id], [VesselRank_Id], [CircularCategories_Id],
            [Langauge_Id], [Circular_Title], [Circular_Description], [Attachment],
            [Circular_Publisher_Date],[Archive_Reason] ,[Auto_Archived_Date],[Archived_By] ,[Circular_Status],[Archive_Date],
            [CreatedDate], [CreatedBy], [ModifiedDate], [ModifiedBy], [IsActive]
        )
        VALUES (
        @Vessels_Id,    @Department_Id, @Vessel, @VesselTypes_Id, @VesselRank_Id, @CircularCategories_Id,
            @Langauge_Id, @Circular_Title, @Circular_Description, @Attachment,
            @Circular_Publisher_Date,@Archive_Reason, @Auto_Archived_Date,@Archived_By, 'Draft',@Archive_Date,
            GETDATE(), @CreatedBy, NULL, NULL, @IsActive
        );
    END

    ELSE IF @Action = 'Update'
    BEGIN
        UPDATE [dbo].[Circular]
        SET 
		  [Vessels_Id] = ISNULL(@Vessels_Id, [Vessels_Id]),
            [Department_Id] = ISNULL(@Department_Id, [Department_Id]),
            [Vessel] = ISNULL(@Vessel, [Vessel]),
            [VesselTypes_Id] = ISNULL(@VesselTypes_Id, [VesselTypes_Id]),
            [VesselRank_Id] = ISNULL(@VesselRank_Id, [VesselRank_Id]),
            [CircularCategories_Id] = ISNULL(@CircularCategories_Id, [CircularCategories_Id]),
            [Langauge_Id] = ISNULL(@Langauge_Id, [Langauge_Id]),
            [Circular_Title] = ISNULL(@Circular_Title, [Circular_Title]),
            [Circular_Description] = ISNULL(@Circular_Description, [Circular_Description]),
            [Attachment] = ISNULL(@Attachment, [Attachment]),
            [Circular_Publisher_Date] = ISNULL(@Circular_Publisher_Date, [Circular_Publisher_Date]),
			[Archive_Reason]=  ISNULL(@Archive_Reason, [Archive_Reason]),
            [Auto_Archived_Date] = ISNULL(@Auto_Archived_Date, [Auto_Archived_Date]),
			[Archived_By]=  ISNULL(@Archived_By, [Archived_By]),
            [Circular_Status] = ISNULL(@Circular_Status, [Circular_Status]),
			[Archive_Date]= ISNULL(@Archive_Date, [Archive_Date]),
            [ModifiedDate] = GETDATE(),
            [ModifiedBy] = ISNULL(@ModifiedBy, [ModifiedBy]),
            [IsActive] = ISNULL(@IsActive, [IsActive])
        WHERE [Circular_Id] = @Circular_Id;
    END

    ELSE IF @Action = 'Delete'
    BEGIN
        UPDATE [dbo].[Circular]
        SET [IsActive] = 0,
            [ModifiedDate] = GETDATE(),
            [ModifiedBy] = @ModifiedBy
        WHERE [Circular_Id] = @Circular_Id;
    END

    ELSE IF @Action = 'GetById'
    BEGIN
        SELECT * FROM [dbo].[Circular] WHERE [Circular_Id] = @Circular_Id AND [IsActive] = 1;
    END

    ELSE IF @Action = 'GetAll'
    BEGIN
        SELECT * FROM [dbo].[Circular] WHERE [IsActive] = 1 Order by Circular_Id desc;
    END

	ELSE IF @Action = 'GetByStatus'
    BEGIN
        SELECT * FROM [dbo].[Circular] 
        WHERE [IsActive] = 1 AND [Circular_Status] = @Circular_Status
        ORDER BY Circular_Id DESC;
    END
END;

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[sp_ManageDocument]
   @Action NVARCHAR(50),  
   @Document_Id INT = NULL,
    @Revision_Id INT = NULL,  
	@Category_Id INT = NULL,
	@SubCategoryString NVARCHAR(MAX) = NULL,
    @Document_Number NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
    @Document_Title NVARCHAR(255) = NULL,
    --@Reference_Number NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
    @Publisher_Date DATETIME = NULL,
    @Valid_From DATETIME = NULL,
   @Document_Applicability NVARCHAR(20) = NULL,
    @Language_Id INT = NULL,
    @VesselRank_Id NVARCHAR(50) = NULL,
    @Vessels_Id NVARCHAR(50) = NULL,
	@VesselTypes_Id NVARCHAR(50) = NULL,
    @Department_Id NVARCHAR(50) = NULL,
    @Author NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
    @Approved_By NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
	@Approved_Date DATETIME = NULL,
    @Document_File_Name NVARCHAR(255) = NULL,
    @Document_Text NVARCHAR(MAX) = NULL,
    @ReviewBy NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
	@Review_Date  DATETIME = NULL,
	@InsertedBy NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
	@Inserted_Date DATETIME = NULL,
    @Status NVARCHAR(50) = NULL,
	@Remarks NVARCHAR(MAX) = NULL,
	@Document_Description NVARCHAR(MAX) = NULL,
	@Current_Version  NVARCHAR(50) = NULL,
	@ChangeInThisVersion NVARCHAR(MAX) = NULL,
	@InternalNotes NVARCHAR(MAX) = NULL,
	@Reference_Title NVARCHAR(MAX) = NULL,
	@Reference_Link NVARCHAR(MAX) = NULL,
    @CreatedDate DATETIME = NULL,
    @CreatedBy NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
    @ModifiedDate DATETIME = NULL,
    @ModifiedBy NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
    @IsActive BIT = NULL
AS
BEGIN
    SET NOCOUNT ON;

    -- Insert a new document
    IF @Action = 'INSERT'
    BEGIN
        INSERT INTO Document 
        (
            Document_Number, Document_Title, Publisher_Date, 
            Valid_From, Language_Id, Author, Approved_By, Document_File_Name, 
            Document_Text, CreatedDate, CreatedBy, IsActive
        )
        VALUES 
        (
            @Document_Number, @Document_Title, @Publisher_Date, 
            @Valid_From, @Language_Id, @Author, @Approved_By, @Document_File_Name, 
            @Document_Text, GETDATE(), @CreatedBy, @IsActive
        );

        SELECT SCOPE_IDENTITY() AS NewDocumentId; -- Return the new document ID
    END

    -- Update an existing document
    ELSE IF @Action = 'UPDATE'
    BEGIN
        UPDATE Document
        SET 
            Document_Number = @Document_Number,
            Document_Title = @Document_Title,
            Publisher_Date = @Publisher_Date,
            Valid_From = @Valid_From,
            Language_Id = @Language_Id,
            Author = @Author,
            Approved_By = @Approved_By,
            Document_File_Name = @Document_File_Name,
            Document_Text = @Document_Text,
            ModifiedDate = GETDATE(),
            ModifiedBy = @ModifiedBy,
            IsActive = @IsActive
        WHERE Document_Id = @Document_Id;
    END

    -- Delete a document
    ELSE IF @Action = 'DELETE'
    BEGIN
        DELETE FROM Document WHERE Document_Id = @Document_Id;
    END

    -- Get all documents
    IF @Action = 'GET_ALL'
BEGIN
    SELECT 
       *
    FROM Document
    ORDER BY Document_Id DESC
END

IF @Action = 'GET_BY_ID'
BEGIN
    SELECT 
      *
    FROM Document
    WHERE Document_Id = @Document_Id ;
END

  ELSE IF @Action = 'GetSubCateWiseRevision'
BEGIN
    SELECT * 
        FROM Document 
        WHERE SubCategoryString = @SubCategoryString 
          AND IsActive = 1 
         END
     ELSE IF @Action = 'DiscardApproved'
    BEGIN
     Update Document set IsActive=0,Status='Discard' WHERE Document_Id = @Document_Id;
    END

    ELSE IF @Action = 'GetDiscardApproved'
BEGIN
    SELECT * FROM Document WHERE SubCategoryString = @SubCategoryString AND IsActive = 0;

    IF @@ROWCOUNT = 0
    BEGIN
        PRINT 'Data not found';
    END
END

END;

CREATE  PROCEDURE [dbo].[sp_ManageInterconnectedManuals]
    @Action NVARCHAR(10),
    @Id INT = NULL,
    @Title NVARCHAR(MAX) = NULL,
    @InternalLinks NVARCHAR(MAX) = NULL,
    @ExternalLinks NVARCHAR(MAX) = NULL,
    @CreatedDate DATETIME = NULL,
    @CreatedBy NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
    @ModifiedDate DATETIME = NULL,
    @ModifiedBy NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
    @IsActive BIT = NULL
AS
BEGIN
    SET NOCOUNT ON;

    -- Insert a new manual
    IF @Action = 'INSERT'
    BEGIN
        INSERT INTO InterconnectedManuals (Title, InternalLinks, ExternalLinks, CreatedDate, CreatedBy, IsActive)
        VALUES (@Title, @InternalLinks, @ExternalLinks, GETDATE(), @CreatedBy, @IsActive);
    END

    -- Update an existing manual
    ELSE IF @Action = 'UPDATE'
    BEGIN
        UPDATE InterconnectedManuals
        SET Title = @Title,
            InternalLinks = @InternalLinks,
            ExternalLinks = @ExternalLinks,
            ModifiedDate = GETDATE(),
            ModifiedBy = @ModifiedBy,
            IsActive = @IsActive
        WHERE Id = @Id;
    END

    -- Soft delete a manual
    ELSE IF @Action = 'DELETE'
    BEGIN
        UPDATE InterconnectedManuals
        SET IsActive = 0,
            ModifiedDate = GETDATE(),
            ModifiedBy = @ModifiedBy
        WHERE Id = @Id;
    END

    -- Get a single manual by Id
    ELSE IF @Action = 'GET_BY_ID'
    BEGIN
        SELECT Id, Title, InternalLinks, ExternalLinks, CreatedDate, CreatedBy, ModifiedDate, ModifiedBy, IsActive
        FROM InterconnectedManuals
        WHERE Id = @Id and IsActive = 1 order by Id desc ;
    END

    -- Get all active manuals
    ELSE IF @Action = 'GET_ALL'
    BEGIN
        SELECT Id, Title, InternalLinks, ExternalLinks, CreatedDate, CreatedBy, ModifiedDate, ModifiedBy, IsActive
        FROM InterconnectedManuals
        WHERE IsActive = 1  order by Id desc;
    END
END;

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[sp_ManageMasters]
    @TableName NVARCHAR(50),  -- Table name (Vessels, Langauge, Departments, VesselRanks)
    @Action NVARCHAR(10),      -- Action (INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE, SELECT)
    @Id INT = NULL,
    @Name NVARCHAR(300) = NULL,
	@ImoNo int =null,
    @CreatedBy NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
    @ModifiedBy NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
    @IsActive BIT = NULL
AS
BEGIN
    SET NOCOUNT ON;

    -- Select Operation
    IF @Action = 'SELECT'
    BEGIN
        IF @TableName = 'Vessels'
            SELECT * FROM Vessels WHERE (@Id IS NULL OR Id = @Id);
        ELSE IF @TableName = 'Langauge'
            SELECT * FROM Langauge WHERE (@Id IS NULL OR Id = @Id);
        ELSE IF @TableName = 'Departments'
            SELECT * FROM Departments WHERE (@Id IS NULL OR Id = @Id);
        ELSE IF @TableName = 'VesselRanks'
            SELECT * FROM VesselRanks WHERE (@Id IS NULL OR Id = @Id);
    END

    -- Insert Operation
    ELSE IF @Action = 'INSERT'
    BEGIN
        IF @TableName = 'Vessels'
            INSERT INTO Vessels (VesselName,ImoNo ,CreatedDate, CreatedBy, IsActive) 
            VALUES (@Name,@ImoNo, GETDATE(), @CreatedBy, @IsActive);

        ELSE IF @TableName = 'Langauge'
            INSERT INTO Langauge (LangaugeName, CreatedDate, CreatedBy, IsActive) 
            VALUES (@Name, GETDATE(), @CreatedBy, @IsActive);

        ELSE IF @TableName = 'Departments'
            INSERT INTO Departments (DepartmentName, CreatedDate, CreatedBy, IsActive) 
            VALUES (@Name, GETDATE(), @CreatedBy, @IsActive);

        ELSE IF @TableName = 'VesselRanks'
            INSERT INTO VesselRanks (VesselRank, CreatedDate, CreatedBy, IsActive) 
            VALUES (@Name, GETDATE(), @CreatedBy, @IsActive);
    END

    -- Update Operation
    ELSE IF @Action = 'UPDATE'
    BEGIN
        IF @TableName = 'Vessels'
            UPDATE Vessels SET VesselName = @Name, ModifiedDate = GETDATE(), ModifiedBy = @ModifiedBy, IsActive = @IsActive WHERE Id = @Id;

        ELSE IF @TableName = 'Langauge'
            UPDATE Langauge SET LangaugeName = @Name, ModifiedDate = GETDATE(), ModifiedBy = @ModifiedBy, IsActive = @IsActive WHERE Id = @Id;

        ELSE IF @TableName = 'Departments'
            UPDATE Departments SET DepartmentName = @Name, ModifiedDate = GETDATE(), ModifiedBy = @ModifiedBy, IsActive = @IsActive WHERE Id = @Id;

        ELSE IF @TableName = 'VesselRanks'
            UPDATE VesselRanks SET VesselRank = @Name, ModifiedDate = GETDATE(), ModifiedBy = @ModifiedBy, IsActive = @IsActive WHERE Id = @Id;
    END

    -- Delete Operation
    ELSE IF @Action = 'DELETE'
    BEGIN
        IF @TableName = 'Vessels'
            DELETE FROM Vessels WHERE Id = @Id;

        ELSE IF @TableName = 'Langauge'
            DELETE FROM Langauge WHERE Id = @Id;

        ELSE IF @TableName = 'Departments'
            DELETE FROM Departments WHERE Id = @Id;

        ELSE IF @TableName = 'VesselRanks'
            DELETE FROM VesselRanks WHERE Id = @Id;
    END
END;

    BEGIN
        INSERT INTO Revision (
            Document_Id,Category_Id,SubCategoryString, Document_Number, Document_Title, Publisher_Date, Valid_From ,Document_Applicability,
            Language_Id, VesselRank_Id, Vessels_Id,VesselTypes_Id, Department_Id, Author, Approved_By,Approved_Date, Document_File_Name,
            Document_Text, ReviewBy,Review_Date,InsertedBy,Inserted_Date, Status,Remarks,Document_Description,Current_Version,ChangeInThisVersion,InternalNotes,Reference_Title,Reference_Link, CreatedDate, CreatedBy, ModifiedDate, ModifiedBy, IsActive
        ) VALUES (
            @Document_Id,@Category_Id,@SubCategoryString, @Document_Number, @Document_Title, @Publisher_Date, @Valid_From, @Document_Applicability,
            @Language_Id, @VesselRank_Id, @Vessels_Id,@VesselTypes_Id, @Department_Id, @Author, @Approved_By,@Approved_Date, @Document_File_Name,
            @Document_Text, @ReviewBy,@Review_Date,@InsertedBy, @Inserted_Date,'Pending',@Remarks,@Document_Description,'1',@ChangeInThisVersion,@InternalNotes,@Reference_Title,@Reference_Link, GETDATE(), @CreatedBy, NULL, NULL, 1
        );
    END

    -- Update Operation
    ELSE IF @Action = 'Update'
BEGIN
    UPDATE Revision
    SET 
        Document_Id = ISNULL(@Document_Id, Document_Id),
        Category_Id = ISNULL(@Category_Id, Category_Id),
        SubCategoryString = ISNULL(@SubCategoryString, SubCategoryString),
        Document_Number = ISNULL(@Document_Number, Document_Number),
        Document_Title = ISNULL(@Document_Title, Document_Title),
        Publisher_Date = ISNULL(@Publisher_Date, Publisher_Date),
        Valid_From = ISNULL(@Valid_From, Valid_From),
		 Document_Applicability = ISNULL(@Document_Applicability, Document_Applicability),
        Language_Id = ISNULL(@Language_Id, Language_Id),
        VesselRank_Id = ISNULL(@VesselRank_Id, VesselRank_Id),
        Vessels_Id = ISNULL(@Vessels_Id, Vessels_Id),
		VesselTypes_Id=ISNULL(@VesselTypes_Id, VesselTypes_Id),
        Department_Id = ISNULL(@Department_Id, Department_Id),
        Author = ISNULL(@Author, Author),
        Approved_By = ISNULL(@Approved_By, Approved_By),
        Approved_Date = ISNULL(@Approved_Date, Approved_Date),
        Document_File_Name = ISNULL(@Document_File_Name, Document_File_Name),
        Document_Text = ISNULL(@Document_Text, Document_Text),
        ReviewBy = ISNULL(@ReviewBy, ReviewBy),
        Review_Date = ISNULL(@Review_Date, Review_Date),
        InsertedBy = ISNULL(@InsertedBy, InsertedBy),
        Inserted_Date = ISNULL(@Inserted_Date, Inserted_Date),
        Status = ISNULL(@Status, Status),
        Remarks = ISNULL(@Remarks, Remarks),
        Document_Description = ISNULL(@Document_Description, Document_Description),
        Current_Version = ISNULL(@Current_Version, Current_Version),
        ChangeInThisVersion = ISNULL(@ChangeInThisVersion, ChangeInThisVersion),
        InternalNotes = ISNULL(@InternalNotes, InternalNotes),
        Reference_Title = ISNULL(@Reference_Title, Reference_Title),
        Reference_Link = ISNULL(@Reference_Link, Reference_Link),
        ModifiedDate = GETDATE(),
        ModifiedBy = @ModifiedBy
    WHERE Revision_Id = @Revision_Id AND IsActive = 1;
END


    -- Delete Operation
    ELSE IF @Action = 'Delete'
    BEGIN

	Update Revision set IsActive=0 WHERE Revision_Id = @Revision_Id;
       -- DELETE FROM Revision WHERE Revision_Id = @Revision_Id;
    END

    -- Get All Records
    ELSE IF @Action = 'GetAll'
    BEGIN
        SELECT * FROM Revision where IsActive=1 and Status='Pending';
    END

    -- Get By Id
    ELSE IF @Action = 'GetById'
    BEGIN
	SELECT * FROM Revision WHERE Revision_Id = @Revision_Id and IsActive=1;
       
    END

	 --ELSE IF @Action = 'GetSubCateWiseRevision'
  --  BEGIN
  --       SELECT * FROM Revision WHERE SubCategoryString = @SubCategoryString and IsActive=1and Status='Pending';
  --  END
  ELSE IF @Action = 'GetSubCateWiseRevision'
BEGIN
    IF @Status = 'Pending'
    BEGIN
        SELECT * 
        FROM Revision 
        WHERE SubCategoryString = @SubCategoryString 
          AND IsActive = 1 
          AND Status in ('Pending' , 'Review');
    END
    ELSE IF @Status = 'Approved'
    BEGIN
        SELECT * 
        FROM Revision 
        WHERE SubCategoryString = @SubCategoryString 
          AND IsActive = 1 
          AND Status = 'Approved' 
    END
    ELSE IF @Status = 'Reject'
    BEGIN
        SELECT * 
        FROM Revision 
        WHERE SubCategoryString = @SubCategoryString 
          AND IsActive = 1 
          AND Status in ('Reject' ,'RejectDiscard');
    END
   
END
ELSE IF @Action = 'RecordofRevision'
BEGIN
    SELECT *  
    FROM Revision  
    WHERE  
       IsActive = 1  
      AND Document_Id =@Document_Id 
END
END

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[sp_ManageSubCategory]
    @Action NVARCHAR(20),  
    @SubCategoryId INT = NULL,
    @CategoryId INT = NULL,
    @CategoryJson NVARCHAR(MAX) = NULL,
	@DashboardView NVARCHAR(MAX) = NULL,
    @CreatedBy NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
    @ModifiedBy NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
    @IsActive BIT = NULL
AS
BEGIN
    SET NOCOUNT ON;

    -- Insert if SubCategoryId doesn't exist, otherwise Update (UPSERT)
    IF @Action = 'UPSERT'
    BEGIN
        MERGE [dbo].[SubCategory] AS target
        USING (SELECT @SubCategoryId AS SubCategoryId) AS source
        ON target.SubCategoryId = source.SubCategoryId

        WHEN MATCHED THEN
            UPDATE SET 
                [CategoryId] = @CategoryId,
                [CategoryJson] = @CategoryJson,
				[DashboardView] = @DashboardView,
                [ModifiedDate] = GETDATE(),
                [ModifiedBy] = @ModifiedBy,
                [IsActive] = @IsActive

        WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
            INSERT ([CategoryId], [CategoryJson],[DashboardView], [CreatedDate], [CreatedBy], [IsActive])
            VALUES (@CategoryId, @CategoryJson,@DashboardView, GETDATE(), @CreatedBy, @IsActive);
    END

    -- Separate Update Action
    ELSE IF @Action = 'UPDATE'
    BEGIN
        UPDATE [dbo].[SubCategory]
        SET 
            [CategoryId] = @CategoryId,
            [CategoryJson] = @CategoryJson,
		    [DashboardView] = @DashboardView,
            [ModifiedDate] = GETDATE(),
            [ModifiedBy] = @ModifiedBy,
            [IsActive] = @IsActive
        WHERE [SubCategoryId] = @SubCategoryId;
    END

    -- Delete SubCategory
    ELSE IF @Action = 'DELETE'
    BEGIN
        --DELETE FROM [dbo].[SubCategory] WHERE [SubCategoryId] = @SubCategoryId;
		update SubCategory set IsActive=0 where SubCategoryId=@SubCategoryId
    END

    -- Get All SubCategories
    ELSE IF @Action = 'GET_ALL'
    BEGIN
        SELECT 
            [SubCategoryId], 
            [CategoryId], 
            [CategoryJson], 
			[DashboardView],
            [CreatedDate], 
            [CreatedBy], 
            [ModifiedDate], 
            [ModifiedBy], 
            [IsActive]
        FROM [dbo].[SubCategory]where IsActive=1;
    END

    -- Get SubCategory by ID
    ELSE IF @Action = 'GET_BY_ID'
    BEGIN
        SELECT 
            [SubCategoryId], 
            [CategoryId], 
            [CategoryJson], 
			[DashboardView],
            [CreatedDate], 
            [CreatedBy], 
            [ModifiedDate], 
            [ModifiedBy], 
            [IsActive]
        FROM [dbo].[SubCategory]
        WHERE [CategoryId] = @SubCategoryId and IsActive=1;
    END

END

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[sp_ManageUser]    Script Date: 3/28/2025 11:25:55 AM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON

SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[sp_ManageUser]
    @Action VARCHAR(20),  
    @UserId INT = NULL,
    @First_Name VARCHAR(50) = NULL,
    @Last_Name VARCHAR(50) = NULL,
	@Department_Id int =NULL,
	@Designation_Id int= NULL,
	@Employee_Id NVARCHAR(100) = NULL,
    @EmailId VARCHAR(200) = NULL,
    @Contact_Number VARCHAR(20) = NULL,
    @Password NVARCHAR(MAX) = NULL,
    @Address VARCHAR(MAX) = NULL,
    @Role VARCHAR(50) = NULL,
    @ProfileImagePath NVARCHAR(MAX) = NULL,
    @CreatedDate DATETIME = NULL,
    @ModifiedDate DATETIME = NULL,
    @IsActive BIT = NULL  
AS
BEGIN
    SET NOCOUNT ON;

    -- Insert user
    IF @Action = 'INSERT'
    BEGIN
        -- Check if the email already exists
        IF EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM UserInfo WHERE EmailId = @EmailId)
        BEGIN
            THROW 50000, 'Email ID already exists.', 1;
            RETURN;
        END

        -- Insert new user
        INSERT INTO [dbo].[UserInfo]
        (
            First_Name, Last_Name,Department_Id,Designation_Id,Employee_Id, EmailId, Contact_Number, Password, 
            Address, Role, ProfileImagePath, CreatedDate, ModifiedDate, IsActive
        )
        VALUES
        (
            @First_Name, @Last_Name,@Department_Id,@Designation_Id,@Employee_Id, @EmailId, @Contact_Number, @Password, 
            @Address, @Role, @ProfileImagePath, @CreatedDate, @ModifiedDate, @IsActive
        );

        -- Return the newly inserted User ID
        SELECT SCOPE_IDENTITY() AS NewUserID;
    END

    -- Update user
    ELSE IF @Action = 'UPDATE'
    BEGIN
        UPDATE UserInfo
        SET
            First_Name = @First_Name,
            Last_Name = @Last_Name,
			Department_Id=@Department_Id,
			Designation_Id=@Designation_Id,
			Employee_Id=@Employee_Id,
            EmailId = @EmailId,
            Contact_Number = @Contact_Number,
            Password = @Password,
            Address = @Address,
            Role = @Role,
            ProfileImagePath = @ProfileImagePath,
            ModifiedDate = @ModifiedDate
        WHERE User_id = @UserId;
    END

    -- Get all users
    ELSE IF @Action = 'GET_ALL'
    BEGIN
        SELECT *
        FROM UserInfo where IsActive=1 order by User_id DESC;
    END

    -- Get user by ID
    ELSE IF @Action = 'GET_BY_ID'
    BEGIN
        SELECT User_id, First_Name, Last_Name,Department_Id,Designation_Id,Employee_Id, EmailId, Contact_Number, 
               Password, Address, ProfileImagePath, CreatedDate, ModifiedDate, IsActive
        FROM UserInfo
        WHERE User_id = @UserId and IsActive=1;
    END

    -- Delete user
    ELSE IF @Action = 'DELETE'
    BEGIN
       -- DELETE FROM UserInfo WHERE User_id = @UserId;
		update UserInfo set IsActive=0 where User_id=@UserId
    END

    -- Invalid action
    ELSE
    BEGIN
        THROW 50000, 'Invalid action specified.', 1;
    END
END

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[sp_ManageVesselTypes]
    @Action NVARCHAR(50),
    @Id INT = NULL,
    @Type NVARCHAR(150) = NULL,
    @CreatedDate DATETIME = NULL,
    @UpdatedDate DATETIME = NULL,
    @DeletedDate DATETIME = NULL,
    @Active BIT = NULL
AS
BEGIN
    SET NOCOUNT ON;

    IF @Action = 'INSERT'
    BEGIN
        INSERT INTO [dbo].[VesselTypes] (Type, CreatedDate, Active)
        VALUES (@Type, GETDATE(), @Active);
    END
    ELSE IF @Action = 'Update'
    BEGIN
        UPDATE [dbo].[VesselTypes]
        SET 
            Type = @Type,
            UpdatedDate = GETDATE(),
            Active = @Active
        WHERE Id = @Id;
    END
    ELSE IF @Action = 'Delete'
    BEGIN
        UPDATE [dbo].[VesselTypes]
        SET 
            DeletedDate = GETDATE(),
            Active = 0
        WHERE Id = @Id;
    END
    ELSE IF @Action = 'GetAll'
    BEGIN
        SELECT Id, Type, CreatedDate, UpdatedDate, DeletedDate, Active
        FROM [dbo].[VesselTypes]
        WHERE Active = 1; -- Only active records
    END
    ELSE IF @Action = 'GetById'
    BEGIN
        SELECT Id, Type, CreatedDate, UpdatedDate, DeletedDate, Active
        FROM [dbo].[VesselTypes]
        WHERE Id = @Id;
    END
END;

/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[sp_MergedDashboardViewJson]    Script Date: 3/28/2025 11:25:55 AM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO


create proc [dbo].[sp_MergedDashboardViewJson]
@CategoryId int,
@SubcategoryString nvarchar(max),
@DocumentPositionJson nvarchar(max)
as

SELECT * 
INTO #tempTbl 
FROM (SELECT * FROM SubCategory WHERE CategoryId = @CategoryId AND IsActive = 1) AS temp;

DECLARE @jsonPath NVARCHAR(500);
DECLARE @subcatstring NVARCHAR(MAX);
DECLARE @dashboardviewMergeJson NVARCHAR(MAX);
DECLARE @subcatname NVARCHAR(200);
DECLARE @json NVARCHAR(MAX);
DECLARE @parentIndex NVARCHAR(10);
DECLARE @childIndex NVARCHAR(10);
DECLARE @parentName NVARCHAR(200);

-- Sample JSON for Subcategories and DashboardView
--SET @subcatstring = '[{"id":"1","name":"Ch.1","manual":false,"description":""},{"id":"2","name":"Policies","manual":true}]';
--SET @dashboardviewMergeJson = '[{"itemId":"item-90","document_Id":11,"revision_Id":90,"document_Title":"test 2 policy","children":[]},{"itemId":"item-89","document_Id":10,"revision_Id":89,"document_Title":"test policy","children":[]}]';

SET @subcatstring =@SubcategoryString;
SET @dashboardviewMergeJson = @DocumentPositionJson;
SELECT @json = DashboardView FROM #tempTbl;

SET @subcatname = (
    SELECT name 
    FROM OPENJSON(@subcatstring)
    WITH (id INT '$.id', name NVARCHAR(255) '$.name', manual BIT '$.manual')
    WHERE manual = 1
);

--PRINT 'Subcategory Name: ' + @subcatname;

-- Find Parent Name Dynamically
SET @parentName = (
    SELECT JSON_VALUE([value], '$.name')
    FROM OPENJSON(@json)
    WHERE JSON_QUERY([value], '$.children') LIKE '%"' + @subcatname + '"%'
);

--PRINT 'Parent Name: ' + @parentName;

-- Get Parent Index dynamically
SELECT TOP 1 @parentIndex = [key]
FROM OPENJSON(@json)
WHERE JSON_VALUE([value], '$.name') = @parentName;

--PRINT 'Parent Index: ' + @parentIndex;

-- Get Child Index dynamically
SET @childIndex = (
    SELECT [key]
    FROM OPENJSON(@json, '$[' + @parentIndex + '].children')
    WHERE LTRIM(RTRIM(JSON_VALUE([value], '$.name'))) COLLATE Latin1_General_CI_AI = @subcatname
);

--PRINT 'Child Index: ' + @childIndex;

-- Construct JSON Path dynamically
SET @jsonPath = '$[' + @parentIndex + '].children[' + @childIndex + '].children';

-- Update JSON in #tempTbl
Update #tempTbl SET DashboardView = JSON_MODIFY(DashboardView, @jsonPath, (SELECT JSON_QUERY(@dashboardviewMergeJson)))
WHERE JSON_VALUE(DashboardView, '$[' + @parentIndex + '].children[' + @childIndex + '].name') = @subcatname;


select * from  #tempTbl;

-- Now update my actual table Subcategory
update SubCategory set DashboardView=(select DashboardView from #tempTbl) where CategoryId=@CategoryId
drop table #tempTbl;

GO
